ures that must be implemented]\n- **Enhanced Features**: [Nice-to-have features for better UX]\n- **Future Enhancements**: [Potential future additions]\n- **Out of Scope**: [What this feature explicitly does NOT do]\n\n## ğŸ—ï¸ Technical Specification\n\n### Component Architecture\n```\n[feature-name]/\nâ”œâ”€â”€ [MainComponent].tsx           # Primary component implementation\nâ”œâ”€â”€ components/\nâ”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ [SubComponent1].tsx      # Supporting components\nâ”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ [SubComponent2].tsx      # Feature-specific UI elements\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ [FormComponent].tsx      # Data input components\nâ”œâ”€â”€ hooks/\nâ”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ use[Feature].ts          # Custom hooks for business logic\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ use[Feature]Data.ts      # Data fetching and state management\nâ”œâ”€â”€ types/\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ [feature].types.ts       # TypeScript type definitions\nâ”œâ”€â”€ utils/\nâ”‚   â””â”€â”€ [feature]-utils.ts       # Utility functions\nâ””â”€â”€ __tests__/\n    â”œâ”€â”€ [MainComponent].test.tsx # Component tests\n    â””â”€â”€ [feature]-utils.test.ts  # Utility tests\n```\n\n### Data Requirements\n\n#### Database Schema\n```sql\n-- Required database tables/modifications\nCREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS [table_name] (\n  id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),\n  user_id UUID REFERENCES profiles(id),\n  [field_name] [data_type] [constraints],\n  created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW(),\n  updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\n-- Required indexes for performance\nCREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_[table]_[field] ON [table_name]([field_name]);\n\n-- RLS policies for security\nALTER TABLE [table_name] ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;\nCREATE POLICY \"Users can manage their own [records]\" ON [table_name]\n  FOR ALL USING (auth.uid() = user_id);\n```\n\n#### API Endpoints\n```typescript\n// Required API routes\n// GET /api/[feature] - Retrieve feature data\n// POST /api/[feature] - Create new records\n// PUT /api/[feature]/[id] - Update existing 